description:
On today’s show, Emily is talking about the benefits of morning sex and position hacks to make sex that much better – as well as taking your calls.

She gives advice on getting past the nerves of dating an old ex without comparing it to the old sex, how to healthily reclaim your life when you are feeling stuck in a sexless marriage, and ways to go about venturing into the world of group sex with your partner of 20 years.
